item.title: Whats Up
item.description: I’been always thinking on writting stuff on the WWW, but never really get full into it, until now, so i would like to give the welcome to what inteend to be be my new blog/site where you can find all about the things that i’m most inerested on, you can expect to find stuff such as Music (mostly punk) Programming (Python, Javascritp, Swift and bit of everything) WWII Podcast RPG games Before digging into different topics i would like Introduce myself, my name is Ethan Escareño Rosano, and i’m from Reynosa, Tamaulipas, Mexico at the moment of writting this post i work as a Software Engineer on different projects around the globe, more exactly on Web Development, but i hope to someday in the short-future start my own startup
